OLED pins   	ESP32 Pins
-------------------------------
GND	          GND
-------------------------------
VCC	          VIN or 3V3
-------------------------------
SCK	          D18 or GPIO18
-------------------------------
SDA	          D23 GPIO23 (MOSI)
-------------------------------
RES	          D4 GPIO4
-------------------------------
DC	          D2 GPIO2
-------------------------------
CS	          D15 GPIO15
-------------------------------




 

